To get the client state for devices belonging to your own organization, the `partnerId` is in the format: `customerId-*anystring*`. Where the `customerId` is your organization's customer ID and `anystring` is any suffix. This suffix is used in setting up Custom Access Levels in Context-Aware Access. You may use `my_customer` instead of the customer ID for devices managed by your own organization.
